    public class PolynomialCalculus<T>
extends Polynomial<T>
    support for calculus on polynomials. polynomial object connected to a power function must have calculus support implemented. the support object makes available derivative and integral methods for calculation using the coefficients. the calculus implementation can support any set of algorithms appropriate to the polynomial type.
    Author:
    Michael Druckman
